flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("", "1AE5B3A8471E2C90D74284A308806359", "A songsheet in the ruins of Nika\'Brae hints of hidden artifact. The song is titled, \'The Dragon\'s Bell\" and tells of the final days of the bard monastery of Nika\'Brae. It fell during the Harbinger Apocalypse, destroyed by a dragon who fought Golgora\'s demons to reach the Bell Tower of Nika\'Brae, where he carried off the great bell. Yet, something was hidden from his dragon intellect, something taken to lair of webs!\"")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("", "E7028DD7462A8BF627EF52AB71B5FBDE", "Find the hidden bard relic in a lair of webs.")
name: CSQ_RVR_0007_BBB_BingBongBrae
